{"tid":769074,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"放榜no offer嘅唔洗擔心","createTime":"2018-08-06T02:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T00:38:13.000Z","uid":42734,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d609ea0effb7b7064d44803309c37d893513d969","tid":769074,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"[能仁推出學費全免/半免學費獎學金計劃]<br />\n<br />\n為鼓勵同學完成本地學士學位課程，能仁推出學費全免/半免學費獎學金計劃。如有DSE 33222 成績報讀本校2018-19年度任何學士學位課程，除獲得政府三萬零八百元資助，其餘學費可獲本校豁免，直至畢業為止，為期四年。<br />\n<br />\n如非DSE 33222 成績入讀，則可獲半免學費的獎學金至畢業為止，為期四年。<br />\n<br />\n此外學院還有其他助學金協助同學，可以減輕學費負擔，專心完成學士學位課程。<br />\n想了解更多，請即致電3996 1000 / 3996 1001 或上網報名 <a href=\"http://ny.edu.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fny.edu.hk&d=POMUm6bgrTSZDVo5mNZtoQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=bcdb5227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ny.edu.hk</a>。<br />\n<br />\n主要學科包括中文，會計，英文，商科，社工。<br />\n<br />\n社工加開傍晚周末班，方便在職人仕。"},{"pid":"3b9f109b2ccfb78fec1fbf59115fe3dbcded51ee","tid":769074,"uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"轉自能仁fb page"},{"pid":"76ff237a4f6c994a4c6a3ebc9f22f43534b07fba","tid":769074,"uid":71543,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:11:06.000Z","msg":"嘩又半價又free 能大但求打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有教無類 同啲學店果然唔係同一個level"},{"pid":"0a1052018a84a45c4aaea23e019970fb0068e777","tid":769074,"uid":108266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:12:02.000Z","msg":"無收DSE咁多年, 請埋你讀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我佛慈悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d22a8d32c9050836079b91130be5a260a4124a","tid":769074,"uid":30186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:12:02.000Z","msg":"搞到我有啲心動想quit u去讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frow